<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7617> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7617" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Listed in RE under Q. Varus (5). The praefectus equitum under Fabius in Gaul in 51, Q. Atius (not Attius) Varus (MRR 2.246) may also be the praefectus under Domitius Calvinus in 48 (Caes. BC 3.37.5; MRR 2.283).\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7617 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7398> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7398" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Envoy in 31. According to Porphyrio on Hor. Sat. 1.4.3, a Q. Varius, whom he confuses with Q. Varius Rufus, was sent by Octavian after the battle of Actium to put Cassius of Parma to death (cf. Veil. 2.87.3; Val. Max. 1.7.7). Possibly Q. Attius Varus (33) and the Q. Varus who was prefect of cavalry in 48 (MRR 2.283). (TJC)\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7398 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5713> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5713" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Prefect of cavalry under Domitius Calvinus (Caes. BC 3.37.5)." ;
	dprr:hasID 5713 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5432> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5432" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Praefectus equitum under Caesar in Gaul (Hirt. in Caes. BG 8.28.2; see 48, Prefects)." ;
	dprr:hasID 5432 .
